comment:
* Base class for implementing a callback for the result of {@link
     * PrintDocumentAdapter#onLayout(PrintAttributes, PrintAttributes,
     * CancellationSignal, LayoutResultCallback, Bundle)}.

methods.name: public void onLayoutFinished(PrintDocumentInfo info, boolean changed)
methods.comment: * Notifies that the layout finished and whether the content changed. * * @param info An info object describing the document. Cannot be null. * @param changed Whether the layout changed. * * @see PrintDocumentInfo

methods.name: public void onLayoutFailed(CharSequence error)
methods.comment: * Notifies that an error occurred while laying out the document. * * @param error The localized error message. * shown to the user. May be null if error is unknown.

methods.name: public void onLayoutCancelled()
methods.comment: * Notifies that layout was cancelled as a result of a cancellation request.

methodNames: public void onLayoutFinished(PrintDocumentInfo info, boolean changed)
